<li><span class="citation book">Goode, Erich; Ben-Yahuda, Nachman (1994). <i>Moral Panics: The Social Construction of Deviance</i>. Cambridge, MA: Wiley-Blackwell. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-631-18905-X" title="Special:BookSources/0-631-18905-X">0-631-18905-X</a>.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Moral+Panics%3A+The+Social+Construction+of+Deviance&amp;rft.aulast=Goode%2C+Erich%3B+Ben-Yahuda%2C+Nachman&amp;rft.au=Goode%2C+Erich%3B+Ben-Yahuda%2C+Nachman&amp;rft.date=1994&amp;rft.place=Cambridge%2C+MA&amp;rft.pub=Wiley-Blackwell&amp;rft.isbn=0-631-18905-X&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Witch-hunt"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
