<li>Purkiss, Diane. "A Holocaust of One's Own: The Myth of the Burning Times." Chapter in <i>The Witch and History: Early Modern and Twentieth Century Representatives</i> New York, NY: Routledge, 1996, pp.&#160;7–29.</li>
